data.description: Just 25 mintues to U of P and 30 minutes to Drexel U, this contemprorary design has a 29 foot deck , Jacuzzi bath tub, Central Air, Fireplace, Private Driveway and IKEA cabinets (rumored to accomodate new IKEA cabinet doors and drawer covers) for a personal touch. Included are recent Washer and Dryer, Refrigerator, and Dishwasher. On the 1st floor enter a foyer featuring formal living room to the right and formal dining room to the left. Next, an island kitchen connects to a family room with fireplace plus sliding glass door to the 29 foot deck.  Also, on the 1st floor find a half bath plus the laundry room.  At the rear, there is a utility shed with components. Upstairs, 4 bedrooms with ample closets, and two (more) full baths with a jacuzzi bathtub,  there are pull down stairs leading to the attic. Finishes include hard wood floors throughout, ceramic tile tubs and showers, and a white pallet for a fresh start. Other pluses include the view straight down Lewis Road at the front of the house and a deeper rear garden view out of the back of the house.
